Seeing as we're sailing into my field (anyone for some mixed metaphors?) here, I think the correlation between personality traits and performance in a footballer's position would be relatively low compared to their technical competence. You could argue for concentration for a keeper and defender, but would be looking for perception, speed of thought, spacial positioning any further forward. 

